=='''Fonduk'''==



==English==

===Etymology===
[[Arabic]] '''فند ق'''   ''fun'duq''

===Pronunciation===
*funduuk or fonduq

==Noun==
'''Fonduk'''

* a Fonduk [''plural'' Fonduks] is a [[North]] [[African]] or an [[Arabian]] [[inn]] or [[hotel]]. Fonduk basically means a hotel in [[Arabic]] but in standard Arabic it means an inn or a [[manor house]]. The word entered the [[English]] [[dictionary]] during the 19th and 20th century. 

